מקלות. Jahve's celestial majesty towers far above all the noisy
majesties here below, whose waves, though lashed never so high, can
still never reach His throne. He is King of His people, Lord of His
church, which preserves His revelation and worships in His temple. This
revelation, by virtue of His unapproachable, all-overpowering kingship,
is inviolable; His testimonies, which minister to the establishment of
His kingdom and promise its future manifestation in glory, are λόγοι
